{"tid":1014043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"客車抄捷徑開上松花江　結果整車凍在河中","createTime":"2019-02-08T22:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T06:18:00.000Z","uid":220701,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b093c4526e45f71cb2fabba1d603c14431574ca9","tid":1014043,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T22:29:30.000Z","msg":"中國黑龍江湯原縣一名巴士駕駛，周四（7日）上午為了省油、省時間，直接把車子開到結冰的松花江上，沒想到才開十多公尺，冰面就整個碎裂，整輛巴士凍在河中。<br />\n<br />\n目擊者表示，駕駛原本載著家人，要去找松花江對岸的親戚拜年，但看到江面已結冰，便決定抄捷徑、直接橫越江面。不料，他才剛開出去十多公尺，冰面就突然碎裂，導致整輛車凍在河中。車上的人後來破窗逃出，沒有人傷亡。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190209/1514459/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190209%2F1514459%2F&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jIxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=a5ab3d4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190209%2F1514459%2F&h=3a6b67f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190209/1514459/</a>"},{"pid":"2b03721cdff97315315d99c6b5904a9197e6c19f","tid":1014043,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T23:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c980cf83618fa9f9bc0e24aa521002e5cef25134","tid":1014043,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T23:23:55.000Z","msg":"睇得卡通多"},{"pid":"f6c1513ede4c54dcf3df1b7c4a58f4db05d6733d","tid":1014043,"uid":83992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T01:10:05.000Z","msg":"一定以為成條河 面到底都結左冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果成部車沉左就好笑 成車死晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c68538223cd2da6d44dea6eda84c010ddb0aee4","tid":1014043,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"